The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, nurse
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros
1. the german is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | singing  |
| Job           | nurse  | designer |
| Nationality   | polish | german   |
| Cigar     | oliveros   | havana |

